1. How to build ?
* make an empty directory as your project root tree
* check out this directory
* check out thirdparty https://tc-scm.tencent.com/setech/setech_infrastructure_rep/Infra_proj/trunk/src/thirdparty
* install blade if not: execute common/builder/blade/install
* install scons if not installed
* blade ... to build

2. Where is the document?
  http://infra.soso.oa.com/mediawiki/index.php/%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB:Common

